Peter Tarsey and his wife Jean were found shot dead with a single bullet each in their sofa in Xalo, near Benidorm . 
  Friends found the couple locked in each other's arms under a green raincoat on Sunday . 
  Mr Tarsey was shot in the back of the neck while his wife was hit in the head . 
  Their sons Alexei and Sascha were also at the house at the time . 
  Police have launched a murder investigation into the deaths . 
  Friend Ann said the couple were found covered in a raincoat . 
  Mr and Mrs Tarsey had been friends for 25 years . 
 